itk-morphologicalcontourinterpolation provides classes to perform image morphological contour interpolation.
Please refer to:
Zukić Dž., Vicory J., McCormick M., Wisse L., Gerig G., Yushkevich P., Aylward S. "nD Morphological Contour Interpolation", Insight Journal, January-December 2016, https://hdl.handle.net/10380/3563.
